snippet.title: Dreamcast Longplay [004] Shenmue II (part 1 of 8)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.net

Played By: RickyC


This is a rip of the dreamcast version. The japanese voices that aren't in cutscenes are mostly missings. quickish run of game though I get a bit lost at the start but its all good. I edited out the times i lost at gambling to speed it up. -
